  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. Running final quality gates and project completion procedure.
  </role>

  <goal>
    Project is marked Complete. All quality gates pass. README, plan.md, CLAUDE.md, and TASK-INDEX.md are updated. Ephemeral notes cleaned. Branch is ready for merge to master via /merge-to-master.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      This is the mandatory final task for the ai-sprk-chat-workspace-companion project. It covers: (1) quality gate validation, (2) repository cleanup, (3) documentation update, (4) lessons learned, and (5) final status verification.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>projects/ai-sprk-chat-workspace-companion/README.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-sprk-chat-workspace-companion/plan.md</file>
