  <steps>
    <step order="1">Run /code-review on all project code — identify and fix any critical issues</step>
    <step order="2">Run /adr-check on all modified files — verify ADR compliance (especially ADR-012 no-Xrm, ADR-021 Fluent v9, ADR-013 write-back constraint)</step>
    <step order="3">Fix any critical issues from steps 1-2 before proceeding</step>
    <step order="4">Run /repo-cleanup projects/ai-sprk-chat-workspace-companion — audit and clean ephemeral files (notes/debug/, notes/spikes/, notes/drafts/)</step>
    <step order="5">Update README.md: Status → "Complete", Last Updated → today, Progress → 100%, Completed Date → today, check all Graduation Criteria boxes, add Changelog entry</step>
    <step order="6">Update plan.md: Status → "Complete", all milestone statuses → ✅</step>
    <step order="7">Update CLAUDE.md: Phase → "Complete", Current Task → "none", Implementation Notes with key learnings</step>
    <step order="8">Create notes/lessons-learned.md with: parallel execution worked well (9 groups), plan_preview SSE design decision, mousedown vs click insight, SPE safety constraint</step>
    <step order="9">Verify all 29 tasks in TASK-INDEX.md are marked ✅ completed</step>
    <step order="10">Run final dotnet test and npm build to confirm no regressions</step>
    <step order="11">Notify user: project complete, ready to run /merge-to-master to merge work/ai-sprk-chat-workspace-companion → master</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="dotnet">Final build and test verification</tool>
    <tool name="npm">Final shared library build verification</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
