    <criterion testable="true">Given /adr-check run on modified files, when ADR-012 no-Xrm constraint is checked, then all shared library components pass.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Given README.md, when Status field is read, then value is "Complete".</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Given TASK-INDEX.md, when all task statuses are read, then all 29 tasks show ✅ completed.</criterion>
