  <notes>
    Key ADR checks to run manually: (1) Grep shared library for 'Xrm' — must return zero matches. (2) Grep WorkingDocumentTools.cs for SPE/Graph write calls — must return zero matches. (3) Verify all Fluent UI token usage in new components (no hard-coded hex colors).
